# \<type\>.sentiment

Sentiment events are divided to two groups - "news" and "social":

Event | Description
--------- | ----------- | -----------
news.sentiment | sentiment data only for articles - aggregated sentiment from news.article events
social.sentiment | sentiment data for other (all social types) entries

Their payload is the same.

